0w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 41}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "张琳芃：是时候结束自己的国家队生涯了，他会选择在什么时机退出国家队，如何评价他为国效力期间的表现？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "北京时间 3 月 21 日，国足在先进两球的情况下痛失好局，最终跟新加坡战平。 赛后国足队长张琳芃情绪有些激动，在混合区面对镜头时表示：「这场比赛我们确实出现了很多问题，首先我作为队长没有改变球队，让球迷失望了，比赛之后我想了很久，我觉得是时候该结束自己的国家队生涯了。」 「连新加坡队我们现在都无法战胜，我觉得这个对于我个人来说是过不去，然后对于我个人来说也是一种耻辱。」张琳芃说。国足队长张琳芃：是时候该结束我的国家队生涯了"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-191455e89dda26ef431d20593ec962b1_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "119 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/649568358"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ij9TImaP4+psREAMaCTEwNjYyNjI4NyCMm/GvBjAAODpABXIJNjQ5NTY4MzU4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1711076930.533716", "card_id": "Q_34769119", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 58}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "医学生看病是一种什么体验？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "116 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/34769119"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0Ij9TImaP4+psREAMaBzYxMTQyNDcg5NLLrgUwADj+AkAGcggzNDc2OTExOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1711076930.534044", "card_id": "Q_266642092", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《还珠格格》中的皇后做过那么多坏事，为什么还有人认为她耿直、三观正呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "《还珠格格》中的皇后没事去漱芳斋找茬打人，后来因为嫉妒紫薇和皇帝下棋对紫薇用针刑；小燕子说出真相后被关进监狱，皇后假传圣旨让宗人府的梁大人拷打小燕子她们并且让她们画押；太后回宫，皇后在太后面前说三道四挑拨离间，把自己包装成受害者；太后要求给香妃换装，皇后却命令嬷嬷们打香妃；令妃生了十五阿哥，紫薇抱着小阿哥，皇后伸脚故意绊倒紫薇；皇帝过寿皇后做了个巫蛊娃娃诅咒皇帝并且借此陷害小燕子紫薇；香妃失踪败露，小燕子紫薇被关进监牢，皇后买通紫薇的舅公舅婆产婆作伪证；小燕子紫薇五阿哥尔康亡命天涯，皇后派杀手打着皇帝的名义要把他们都杀死。这些事情都是皇后做的，为什么还有人都认为皇后是正常人、是好人，值得同情呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-9d48e2edbc4cb63c7c3c3ee3879a4b03_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "97 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/266642092"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ij9TImaP4+psREAMaCDIxMDg5MDU0IJ2G2NMFMAA4OEAHcgkyNjY2NDIwOTJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1711076930.534603", "card_id": "Q_649565688", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 47}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "国足客场遭新加坡逼平，如何评价主教练伊万科维奇的表现？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-9939e0e8ac8e16fb33dc5c1f0a2f5353_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "96 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/649565688"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ij9TImaP4+psREAMaCTEwNjYyNTcwNCDgi/GvBjAAODVACHIJNjQ5NTY1Njg4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1711076930.534879", "card_id": "Q_649493380", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1006}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价网飞版《三体》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhi